<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../lib/bootstrap-3.3.5-dist/css/bootstrap.css">
    <style>
        body{
            background: url("../images/b413f1c448f99f5c1b1e8bd360ae6c15.jpg") fixed;
            background-size: 100% 100%;
        }
        .goods_footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        ul > li {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        h3 {
            padding-left: 30px;
        }

        .goods_jiesao {
            margin-top: 100px;
            height: 200px;
            display: table-cell;
            vertical-align: middle;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .goods_footer_biaoti {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer_image1 {
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            height: 200px;
        }

        .footer_image1 img {
            height: 300px;
        }

        .goods_mingxing {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .goods_jiage1 {
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .goods_mingxing img {
            width: 190px;
            height: 250px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .section > ul {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        #mingxing {
            border: #E0E0E0 solid 8px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        #wenzi{
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 50px;
            padding-left: 30px;
            padding-right: 30px;
            height: 300px;
            background-color: #E9E9E9;
            color: #B0A8A1;
        }
        #wenzi2{
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .goods_mingxing3{
            text-align: center;
            border:#E0E0E0 solid 8px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .goods_mingxing3 img {
            width: 200px;
            height: 250px;
        }
        #xuanranGoods{
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
<%- include("./common/header.ejs") %>
<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-2 col-lg-offset-2 goods_footer">
            <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked">
                <h4><a>面部</a></h4>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">卸妆</a></li>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">洁面</a></li>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">化妆水</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked">
                <h4><a>身体护理</a></h4>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">保湿滋润</a></li>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">去除角质</a></li>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">塑身纤体</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked">
                <h4><a>防嗮</a></h4>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">面部防晒</a></li>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">身体防晒</a></li>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">晒后护理</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked">
                <h4><a>肌肤问题</a></h4>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">抗皱御龄</a></li>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">紧致提拉</a></li>
                <li class="tiao"><a href="#">亮泽美白</a></li>

            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 neirong">
            <h2>护肤</h2>
            <hr>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 footer_image1">
                    <img src="../images/categorie-soin-image_1.jpg" class="col-lg-12">
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-8 goods_jiesao">
                    <div>为满足不同的肌肤需求，解决各种复杂的肌肤问题，法国希思黎为您提
                        供一系列周全的专属美容护肤产品：卸妆、清洁、补水、保湿、抗老、
                        防晒以及头发护理等。法国希思黎的研发专家不仅深谙各种植物成分及
                        其作用于肌肤的效果，还熟知皮肤机能的奥秘，将它们完美地结合在一
                        起，融汇成了法国希思黎独树一帜的专业护肤理念。
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row " id="mingxing">

                <div class="col-lg-12 goods_footer_biaoti">
                    法国希思黎明星产品
                </div>
                <% data[4].forEach((item)=>{ %>
                <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                    <img src="../images/<%= item.d_smallSrc %>">
                    <div><%= item.g_name %></div>
                    <div class="goods_jiage1">明星产品</div>
                    <div class="goods_jiage1">￥<%= item.d_price %></div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">查看产品</a></button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">点击购买</a></button>
                </div>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
            <div class="row section">
                <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
                    <li role="presentation" class="active"><a href="#home" aria-controls="home" role="tab"
                                                              data-toggle="tab">面部</a></li>
                    <li role="presentation"><a href="#profile" aria-controls="profile" role="tab"
                                               data-toggle="tab">身体护理</a></li>
                    <li role="presentation"><a href="#messages" aria-controls="messages" role="tab"
                                               data-toggle="tab">防嗮</a></li>
                    <li role="presentation"><a href="#settings" aria-controls="settings" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">肌肤问题</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-lg-offset-9 dropdown">
                    分 类：
                    <select id="paixu1">
                        <option>价格</option>
                        <option value="1">价格从低到高</option>
                        <option value="2">价格从高到低</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <!-- Tab panes -->
                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane active" id="home">
                        <div class="row paixu" id="xuanranGoods">
                            <% data[0].forEach((item)=>{ %>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                                <div><img src="../images/<%= item.d_smallSrc %>"></div>
                                <p><%= item.g_name %></p>
                                <p><%= item.g_descript %></p>
                                <p>￥<%= item.d_price %></p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">查看产品</a>
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">点击购买</a>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <% }) %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="profile">
                        <div class="row" id="xuanranGoods">
                            <% data[1].forEach((item)=>{ %>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                                <div><img src="../images/<%= item.d_smallSrc %>"></div>
                                <p><%= item.g_name %></p>
                                <p><%= item.g_descript %></p>
                                <p>￥<%= item.d_price %></p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">查看产品</a>
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">点击购买</a>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <% }) %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="messages">
                        <div class="row" id="xuanranGoods">
                            <% data[2].forEach((item)=>{ %>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                                <div><img src="../images/<%= item.d_smallSrc %>"></div>
                                <p><%= item.g_name %></p>
                                <p><%= item.g_descript %></p>
                                <p>￥<%= item.d_price %></p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">查看产品</a>
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">点击购买</a>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <% }) %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="settings">
                        <div class="row" id="xuanranGoods">
                            <% data[3].forEach((item)=>{ %>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                                <div><img src="../images/<%= item.d_smallSrc %>"></div>
                                <p><%= item.g_name %></p>
                                <p><%= item.g_descript %></p>
                                <p>￥<%= item.d_price %></p>
                                <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">查看产品</a>
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=<%= item.d_id %>">点击购买</a>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <% }) %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-lg-offset-9">
            <ul class="pagination">
                <li>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Previous">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li><a href="#">1</a></li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#" aria-label="Next">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&raquo;</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<%- include("./common/footer.ejs") %>
<script src="../lib/bootstrap-3.3.5-dist/js/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
<script src="../lib/bootstrap-3.3.5-dist/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
<script>
    $("#paixu1").on("change", function () {
        let p=this;
        $.ajax({
            type: "get",
            url: "/search.do",
            data: {},
            success(arr) {
                if ($(p).val()==1) {
                    $(".paixu").html("")
                    arr[0].forEach((item, index) => {
                        $(".paixu").append(`
                        <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                            <div><img src="../images/${item['d_smallSrc']}"></div>
                            <p>${item['g_name']}</p>
                            <p>${item.g_descript}</p>
                            <p>${ item.d_price}</p>

                            <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=${item.d_id}">查看产品</a></button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=${item.d_id}">点击购买</a></button>

                    </div>`)
                    })
                }
                if ($(p).val()== 2) {
                    $(".paixu").html("")
                    arr[1].forEach((item, index) => {
                        $(".paixu").append(`
                        <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                            <div><img src="../images/${item['d_smallSrc']}"></div>
                            <p>${item['g_name']}</p>
                            <p>${item.g_descript}</p>
                            <p>${ item.d_price}</p>
                            <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=${item.d_id}">查看产品</a></button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=${item.d_id}">点击购买</a></button>
                    </div>`)
                    })
                }
            }
        })
    })
    $(".tiao").on("click", function () {
        let wenzi= $(this).text();
        console.log(wenzi);
        $.ajax({
            type: "get",
            url: "/getgoodxuanran.do",
            data: {
                wenzi
            },
            success(arr) {
             console.log(arr)
                $(".neirong").html("")
                arr[0].forEach((item, index) => {
                    $(".neirong").append(`
                     <h4>${item['category_name']}</h4>
            <div>
                ${item['category_info']}
            </div>
            `)
                })
                arr[1].forEach((item,index) =>{
                    $(".neirong").append(`
                    <div class="row" >
                <div class="col-lg-6 goods_mingxing3">
                    <div><img src="../images/${item.d_smallSrc}"></div>
                    <p>${item.g_name}</p>
                    <p>${item.g_descript}</p>
                    <p>${item.d_price}</p>
                    <p id="wenzi2">卸除彩妆，为干性和敏感性肌肤带来柔嫩体验。</p>
                    <button type="button" class="btn"><a href="details?id=${item.d_id}">查看产品</a></button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=${item.d_id}">点击购买</a></button>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-1">
                    <div id="wenzi">
                        本品质地柔滑，可有效溶解彩妆，同时为干性和敏感性肌肤保持平衡。其配方中富含白百合精华，快速营造出舒适感受。肌肤柔嫩有弹性，莹润明亮。
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                    `)
                })
                $(".neirong").append(`
                <div class="row" id="xuanranGoods">
                </div>
                `)
                arr[2].forEach((item,index) =>{
                    $("#xuanranGoods").append(`
                <div class="col-lg-4 goods_mingxing">
                    <div><img src="../images/${item.d_smallSrc}"></div>
                    <p>${item.g_name}</p>
                    <p>${item.g_descript}</p>
                    <p>${item.d_price}</p>
                    <button type="button" class="btn"><a href="details?id=${item.d_id}">查看产品</a></button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn "><a href="details?id=${item.d_id}">点击购买</a></button>
                </div>

                    `)
                })
            }
        })
    })
</script>
</body>
</html>